.
</paragraph>
<paragraph blockId="56.[189,1399,532,629]" pageId="56" pageNumber="57">HEAD. Ratio width of vertex at anterior ocellus: width of head 1: 3.6; ratio width of ocellar triangle: width of vertex 1: 2.5; ratio length of ocellar triangle: length of frons 1: 3.3. Mouth edge narrowly brown. Basoflagellomere oval, ratio width: length 1: 1.4, about 3.5 times as long as basoflagellomere.</paragraph>
<caption ID-DOI="http://doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.3830585" ID-Zenodo-Dep="3830585" httpUri="https://zenodo.org/record/3830585/files/figure.png" pageId="56" pageNumber="57" startId="56.[189,232,1929,1955]" targetBox="[200,1388,760,1896]" targetPageId="56">
