. 
<emphasis bold="true" box="[990,1011,1929,1955]" pageId="56" pageNumber="57">A</emphasis>
. Posterior part of abdomen, left side, lateral view. 
<emphasis bold="true" box="[409,429,1964,1990]" pageId="56" pageNumber="57">B</emphasis>
. Sternum IV, ventral view. 
<emphasis bold="true" box="[763,784,1964,1990]" pageId="56" pageNumber="57">C</emphasis>
