<emphasis bold="true" box="[1376,1398,504,530]" italics="true" pageId="57" pageNumber="58">⅓</emphasis>
yellow; sternum III elongate, ratio width: length 1: 2.8; sternum IV trapezoid, ratio width: length 1: 1.0; sternum V rectangular, with crenelated posterior margin, ratio width: length 1: 1.2.
</paragraph>
